{"tid":1088793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那再傳爆炸意外 上午大檢查...下午安徽化工廠秒起火打臉","createTime":"2019-04-02T09:55:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T11:17:58.000Z","uid":32511,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f6dc5c2175b6bddb60c78d9cac4cea6dd0e8e001","tid":1088793,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T09:55:14.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=94tmr1XWRMg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D94tmr1XWRMg&d=mFE05qKCD2WHpL72sA8m68v4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=df72212e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=94tmr1XWRMg</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n中國近期工廠爆炸意外不斷，昨下午再傳安徽省化工廠爆炸意外，現場火勢猛烈、濃煙直竄，所幸皆無人員傷亡，令人傻眼的是，在爆炸當日上午，中國當局曾在微博發出，為記取江蘇化工廠爆炸的教訓，全面對化工企業進行消防安全大檢查的貼文，引起網友不滿。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，昨下午3點多安馬鞍山市慈湖地區一間化工廠再傳爆炸意外，影片中可見工廠火勢不小、冒出大量濃煙，經初步研判是因為廠區的化學材料著火才會導致火災，火勢在2小時內控制住，並無人員傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n據《新浪網》報導，最諷刺的是昨日上午馬鞍山市人民政府才在微博貼出政務要聞，表示要記取江蘇化工廠爆炸的教訓，連日來消防救援支隊以整治火災隱患，全面對化工廠進行消防大檢查，但此文一出後下午就再度傳來化工廠爆炸意外。<br />\n<br />\n網友紛紛回應「這文似乎有一絲絲尷尬」、「打臉真快，不知道是不是做做樣子」、「不說客套話了，多做點事吧」、「趕緊摀臉，要不然臉會腫的」、「務實一點吧政府部門」。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，該起爆炸意外已經是中國這2週內第5起工廠爆炸事故，先前最嚴重的2次爆炸意外分別發生在江蘇鹽城響水縣及江蘇崑山市，其中江蘇鹽城響水縣的化工廠爆炸更導致至少78人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpDggkhX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpDggkhX.jpg&h=6950144b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3a9c8c161e0f82e3423e7b3922916d878ef4a71","tid":1088793,"uid":180576,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T11:06:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">所幸皆無人員傷亡</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b32102d0908aaa7604194cd25cd5ce10ed497c19","tid":1088793,"uid":73340,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T11:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AiRQHSm.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAiRQHSm.gif&h=8d90ba5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f84ce38efea38b3e5accff3d855eaff0e75c2d5c","tid":1088793,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T11:08:43.000Z","msg":"銀牙銀牙銀牙銀牙銀牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30782a008cf4a760379ddfb9d02f4719137a7726","tid":1088793,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T11:09:18.000Z","msg":"並無傷亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1a408eb1238acaf954aefb7d3786d48cf07f2cf","tid":1088793,"uid":19660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T11:10:35.000Z","msg":"檢查完即刻疏散晒先冇人傷亡<br />\n<br />\n要多謝黨了"},{"pid":"e09df188e98db30ad44fedc20466f809ca4298ef","tid":1088793,"uid":9215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b32102d0908aaa7604194cd25cd5ce10ed497c19","tid":1088793,"uid":73340,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T11:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AiRQHSm.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAiRQHSm.gif&h=8d90ba5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T11:12:35.000Z","msg":"seed or mother?"},{"pid":"c71e250e7794e62dee9ee90492f7968e76a217b9","tid":1088793,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e09df188e98db30ad44fedc20466f809ca4298ef","tid":1088793,"uid":9215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b32102d0908aaa7604194cd25cd5ce10ed497c19","tid":1088793,"uid":73340,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T11:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AiRQHSm.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAiRQHSm.gif&h=8d90ba5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T11:12:35.000Z","msg":"seed or mother?"},"citedBy":0,"replyT